Welcome to the InterSpread help. This is not intended to replace the manual
but suplement it by giving a discription of most of InterSpreads functions.
For a more acurate and verboise description of InterSpread's functions it
is recomended that you consult your manual.

		Table of contents


 
@{" Introduction                          " link "IntroText"}
@{" Description of mathematical functions " link "APPENDIX B"}
@{" Descriptions of menus                 " link "APPENDIX C"}
