@{"SET_CURRENT_CELL_VALUE" link "SET_CURRENT_CELL_VALUE"}
@{"SHEETNAME" link "SHEETNAME"}
@{"SHEETPATH" link "SHEETPATH"}
@{"SORRYREQ" link "SORRYREQ"}
@{"STRREQ" link "STRREQ"}

AREXX MENU COMMANDS
The ARexx commands listed in this section primarily duplicate menu
functions. Therefore, rather than repeating what has already been written
in the menu descriptions , this section just lists a brief summary of
each command. For more complete details about the function of each
